{"tid":150083,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港麥當勞即將變革，新系列套餐40元起","createTime":"2017-03-09T18:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T03:36:57.000Z","uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"715e105f6dcff858f1d84c4658a5414654fe169e","tid":150083,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j4M3E9Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj4M3E9Y.jpg&h=63b8af50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港麥當勞即將變革，分店會陸續加入新元素，除了在裝潢上作出改動，以黑、白、黃為主色調外，亦會新增餐飲和其他顧客服務。<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞由3月9日起，將於全線推出新系列The Signature Collection；此系列其實曾於2016年在部份分店試賣，反應不錯，現在正式推出並列為長期供應食品，食材也調整了一點，率先睇睇各款配搭！<br />\n<br />\n3款漢堡的主角分別為「特厚100%安格斯牛肉」、「香烤原塊雞腿」、「秘製Buttermilk炸雞」，配搭不同種類的麵包，包括Bagel、法式甜包、意式軟包。<br />\n<br />\n自選My Signature系列可以自由組合以上各款食材；全個系列，包括漢堡包包裝紙和薯條盒都換上新包裝，價錢40元起。"},{"pid":"c4dcc30607e9cef535882a8cdb7aa58c6ab68106","tid":150083,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:17:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"a717c761f5caa8e29a198c8657ee8faf22676b9a","tid":150083,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:18:25.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"672cb154e003bff7761ec9fe9532538796dccb7d","tid":150083,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:22:34.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"edabbb92f231f72f4e5fdf046767fe5f30dcd309","tid":150083,"uid":4576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食mos burger好過"},{"pid":"fa654dc74fbe2c6a6020588cf5570853ec74b2be","tid":150083,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:28:52.000Z","msg":"食貴價burger我做咩要揀m記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84038fdbe70d8f4115cda37931a128be890ea368","tid":150083,"uid":45773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited